# ============================================
# Night Tavern - GitHub Distribution Setup
# ============================================
# This repo only tracks documentation files.
# Unity project files are distributed via GitHub Releases.
# Full project is managed in Unity Cloud.
# ============================================

# Ignore EVERYTHING by default
*

# ============================================
# KEEP: Documentation files for GitHub
# ============================================
!.gitignore
!README.md
!LICENSE
!CHANGELOG.md

# Keep docs folder and its contents
!docs/
!docs/**

# ============================================
# Ignore build artifacts and local scripts
# ============================================
releases/
scripts/

# ============================================
# Ignore system files even in kept folders
# ============================================
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.log

# Keep Scripts folder and its contents
!Assets/Scripts/
!Assets/Scripts/**
!Assets/Scripts/Xybrid/
!Assets/Scripts/Xybrid/**